                <head>266. Minutes of a Policy Review Committee Meeting<note n="1" type="source"
                        xml:id="d266fn1">Source: <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName>
                        Library, National Security Council, Institutional Files, Box 60, <gloss
                            target="#t_PRC_2">PRC</gloss> 008, Latin America 3/23/77. Secret. The
                        meeting took place in the White House Situation Room. The minutes are
                        scheduled to be printed in full in <ref target="frus1977-80v24">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations,</hi> 1977–1980, vol. XXIV, South
